metadata.name: Jean Michel - Pride Series Foundation #1
metadata.description:
A series of ASCII + Pixel Art creations, delivered as 2D images or MP4 videos, made by MagnaK . Inspired in famous personalities, writers, artists, and characters, who in their times and environments were or are example of diversity. Honoring all of them in the year 2022 at the Pride month!
5417 x 6750 pixels @ 300dpi
